Key.English: Cleans up dead objects and improves performance
Key.Chinesesimp: 清除死亡对象并提高性能

Key.English: Include certain non-unit or non-vehicle objects in collection eg: ["Box_NATO_Wps_F","Box_NATO_AmmoOrd_F"]
Key.Chinesesimp: 在集合中包含某些非单位或非车辆对象,例如:["Box_NATO_Wps_F","Box_NATO_AmmoOrd_F"]

Key.English: Interval in which to clean killed objects! Use 0 to turn off GC completely!
Key.Chinesesimp: 清理已杀死对象的时间间隔!使用0完全关闭GC!

Key.English: Will remove all dead objects and groups if this limit is met (count allDead)
Key.Chinesesimp: 如果满足此限制，将删除所有死亡的对象和组(计数allDead)
